The All Progressives Congress (APC) has postponed the screening excercise for its presidential aspirants till further notice. The exercise was earlier scheduled to hold on Monday, May 23, 2022. A terse statement signed by the National Publicity Secretary of APC, Barr. Felix Morka, on Sunday night, said, “A new date for the exercise will be announced shortly. “Any inconvenience caused is deeply regretted.”